      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Sun-born ifrits sometimes inherit their stellar progenitor&rsquo;s nuclear nature. An ifrit of 5th level or higher with this trait can cast @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.vOQ1NkfDHafdqTfE]{Irradiate} once per day. At 12th level, they can use this ability one additional time per day. Their caster level equals their level, and the save DC is equal to 13 + their Charisma modifier.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces an ifrit&rsquo;s spell-like ability.</strong></p>\n<p><em><br />After adding the spell to the Spellbook tab, edit the spell's Details, changing the Spell Preparation Mode to Innate Spellcasting, and change Limited uses to x of x Day as level allows.</em><strong><br /></strong></p>"
